<input type='number' min='12' max='96' name='order[frame][length]'><label>inches</label></fieldset>
</fieldset> 

<fieldset><legend>                                                           
<select name='order[bench][style]'>
<option value='no'>no</option>                                               
<option value='sd'>sd</option>                                               
<option value='hd'>hd</option>                                               
</select> <span>bench</span>                                         
</legend>
<p>What is the length from the end of one arm rest, across the back and to the end of the other arm rest?</p>
